    "name": "Pet Shop Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 2401680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营宠物店</strong></h2>你在宠物店模拟游戏中的主要任务是经营宠物店。你的职责不仅包括为动物们寻找美好的新家，还要确保它们能过上幸福的生活。因此，为你的宠物店补充合适的产品，以便你在送出宠物时为它们提供合适的产品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/47379eaeaa905648a4bbabdba4f93a1b.poster.avif?t=1757497376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/47379eaeaa905648a4bbabdba4f93a1b.webm?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/47379eaeaa905648a4bbabdba4f93a1b.mp4?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让客户梦想成真</strong></h2>各种顾客都会光顾你的宠物店。从老人到有孩子的父母或学生。他们每个人都会对其想要照顾和爱护的宠物有特定的偏好。你的职责是让他们梦想成真，并为宠物找到完美的家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/ac7e1d366afe411695f972992e8eca77.poster.avif?t=1757497376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/ac7e1d366afe411695f972992e8eca77.webm?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/ac7e1d366afe411695f972992e8eca77.mp4?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>请确保拥有适合你宠物的装备</strong></h2>为你的客户挑选合适的宠物，但这并不是你工作的全部。为每只宠物提供合适的食物、设备和配件产品，也同样重要。你必须确保为你的宠物选择合适的笼子尺寸，并提供最好的食物、梳理毛发的刷子，还有玩具和零食。每一个细节都将转化为宠物的幸福，和新主人的所学到的知识！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/eefbaf121a7d2aa79004fdacc49cf60f.poster.avif?t=1757497376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/eefbaf121a7d2aa79004fdacc49cf60f.webm?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/eefbaf121a7d2aa79004fdacc49cf60f.mp4?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理和照顾好你的宠物店</strong></h2>作为宠物店老板，在本游戏中等待你的挑战之一就是妥善管理好整家宠物店。根据客户要求，检查商店的种类、下订单、进口专用设备。妥善管理业务会给你带来众多优势，同时也能让你为宠物找到完美的家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/dde6de1912c743105f78add57161a400.poster.avif?t=1757497376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/dde6de1912c743105f78add57161a400.webm?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/dde6de1912c743105f78add57161a400.mp4?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发展你的宠物业务</strong></h2>管理和发展你的宠物店，不断扩大其面积、功能和宠物品种。照顾好你的客户，并重视他们的意见，在附近购买新物业，进一步发展你的业务！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/df758d2d914f6a9c8a0277226314abd8.poster.avif?t=1757497376\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/df758d2d914f6a9c8a0277226314abd8.webm?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401680/extras/df758d2d914f6a9c8a0277226314abd8.mp4?t=1757497376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
